<p>This is not a replacement for traditional SEO. It is an expansion. Google still drives the most <a href="/glossary/organic-traffic/">organic traffic</a> for most businesses. But Google alone leaves significant visibility on the table.</p>
<p>The key distinction: traditional SEO optimizes one channel deeply. Search Everywhere Optimization maintains presence across channels strategically.</p>
